<p class="">Did not the Resolution of the Security Council of 29th May, to which my right hon. Friend referred, place an embargo on the introduction of military personnel into these States?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c9bfc7f8-d4af-404b-8e37-fa36448fee97" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
