<p class="">I certainly did not stake my political reputation upon the successes which those generals would have, but I think the day will come when it will be recognised without doubt, not only on one side of the House but throughout the civilised world, that the strangling of Bolshevism at its birth would have been an untold blessing to the human race.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
