    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, it would have prevented the last war.<p></p> Let me return to the more peaceful paths of Palestine and leave these furious controversies of a bygone period. When this Anglo-American Committee reported, its recommendations, although accepted by Mr. Truman, were rejected by His Majesty's Government.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
