<p class="">Were not the Arabs continually importing arms? And, what is worse, importing them from this country?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-875df71a-392c-489d-99ee-8330db260fd0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
