    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">During the past three years I have had many opportunities, I sometimes think too many opportunities, of listening to the hon. Member for Nelson and Colne (Mr. S. Silverman) intervening in Debate. I always failed to agree with him but, up to now, I have always succeeded in understanding him. Tonight I have failed. I could not understand the reason <span id="1042" class="column-number" data-column-number="1042"></span> why he would have voted against the Government on any other occasion had a vote been taken, but on this one occasion when a vote is to be taken he feels unable to do so.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0f48cf99-b164-4146-b5cd-dfc5dc12dacd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
