<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-99e75ccd-08cc-4da6-99df-bf6a2ab72585'>
            
<p class="">manoeuvre of the right hon. Gentleman in which, by working on the natural feelings of people, who are very much worked up on this, he hopes to snatch a victory for the Conservative Party. Anyone on this side of the House who knows the Conservative Party with its record of always being in the wrong, sees that here we have a party manoeuvre by the right hon. Gentleman. In this matter, of course, a vote on the Adjournment is a vote of confidence in the Government. I am quite sure we shall get that vote in ample measure.</p>
        </div>
